author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-ARM says its smartphone outlook unchanged, has robust licensing pipeline
text:
Oct 21 Arm Holdings Plc
* Cfo says "no means out" of a v8 licencing cycle, says "pipeline robust"
* Cfo says global smartphone outlook for 2016 unchanged, sees continued outperformance Further company coverage: (Reporting By London Bureau)
